model.hed: See the Entire 2015 GQ for Gap Best New Menswear Designers in America Collection
model.dek: The wait is almost over. On September 29, our latest collection for Gap, created by the [BNMDA](http://www.gq.com/story/gq-bnmda-gap-collection-preview-video-2015) class of 2015 will hit the web and stores across the country. Past collections have sold out fast, so get your game plan in order. Here, take a look at what the menswear geniuses at David Hart, Stampd, [NSF](http://www.gq.com/gallery/10-essentials-nsf), and [The Hill-Side](http://www.gq.com/story/the-hill-side) have created. It's everything you need to look your absolute best this fall, all in one place. See you at the Gap.
